&lt;p&gt;Check the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/dillonzq/LoveIt/blob/master/LICENSE&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer&#34;&gt;LICENSE file&lt;/a&gt;
